{"tid":1399493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【8月5大罷工大罷市總攻略】推上熱門 歡迎補充 重推畀更加多人知","createTime":"2019-08-03T07:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:53:04.000Z","uid":264783,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be8c2950468801db2033884d2f9814ff5b53c64d","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"訴求未達&middot; 全港三罷<br />\n8月5日 七區開花<br />\n罷工罷課罷市<br />\n<br />\n當日早上7點開始全港性不合作運動(越早越好) <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎早到 拒絕遲到</span></span><br />\n港鐵:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">荔景 鑽石山 炮台山站</span></span><br />\n以及堵塞主要道路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">塞鐵tg:<a href=\"http://t.me/mstopthem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmstopthem&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=0066683c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/mstopthem</a></span><br />\n<br />\n1200 圍堵7區政府合署及稅局 幫公務員收工 (因為佢地1230放lunch)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎早到拒絕遲到</span></span><br />\n七區開花詳情及開始時間:<br />\n<br />\n金鐘  添馬公園  13:00<br />\n旺角  麥花臣  13:00<br />\n黃大仙  黃大仙廣場  13:00<br />\n沙田  百步梯  13:00<br />\n大埔  大埔風水廣場  13:00<br />\n荃灣  荃灣公園  13:00<br />\n屯門  政府綜合大樓對出空地 <br />\n          1500<br />\n<br />\n(部分活動詳情與有關部門溝通中)<br />\n<br />\n#香港是我家三罷齊參加<br />\n#反逃犯條例修訂 <br />\n#五大訴求 <br />\n#罷工罷課罷市 <br />\n#85HKonStrike <br />\n#85strike<br />\n<br />\nTg channel :@saveinghk<br />\nTg group:@saveinghkgrp<br />\n<br />\n塞鐵重點：<br />\n<br />\n805 鑽山炮山荔景 塞鐵<br />\n⭕️綠線：鑽石山站塞左九龍塘要出中環既人<br />\n⭕️紅線：荔景結構問題可以成條紅線出唔到中環<br />\n⭕️藍線：炮台山就塞埋走將軍澳線去中環既人<br />\n去邊個站自己決定❗️<br />\n目標❌商業區，係唔比佢地去商業區！<br />\n<br />\n❌唔直接塞大站原因❌<br />\n❎多增援<br />\n❎月台大 狗鐵好快出後備方案<br />\n✅塞細站 動員更少成效更大<br />\n✅需要極多手足<br />\n❌重點癱瘓商業區<br />\n重申塞鐵tg: <a href=\"http://t.me/mstopthem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmstopthem&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=0066683c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/mstopthem</a><br />\n<br />\n朝早塞鐵同接放工並唔會阻礙到下午嘅五區集會， 煩請所有為香港出力罷工罷學嘅市民一齊同心做多一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要係朝早見曬你哋全部<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125b64359d82fa2b9e41698800f39e9c0041349e","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dea7501a377155cdff3deaa96233668060aff9c","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a78c027e29dd08e397d1787e6c67adcbaa80deac","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"4bdedcfec4feeace3e7e71239c3ad4ca3345ee63","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"再再自推"},{"pid":"5321219fa12a123724fe79c692c4689422c1dde3","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27a8ad4bd75180c3b18bba9c8a601eb6c1bf877","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"十連都要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b76153e75567f0170b2c942028d08f49c72ae5","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da302a3247eb23077b6fe58f991f51e15c236d43","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:41:21.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8494240abbce0dc7354ddb863e306ce623c9c9dd","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:41:53.000Z","msg":"share俾你啲朋友知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44feaf6d31f833bc0a96ba001d451195cddbce2b","tid":1399493,"uid":277873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"樓主漏咗<br />\n八五罷工仲必須要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拒絕消費</span></span></strong><br />\n就算有人個日唔罷工開舖，都唔會做到生意<br />\n咁先真係有效架.......<br />\n麻煩大家聽日都預備定週一既早午晚飲食安排<br />\n唔係個個罷工轉頭去幫趁啲唔罷既藍絲食肆我就真係無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de663ae01eb8d8aba3b490ff6356439d8d05b2d7","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmGfeDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmGfeDT.jpg&h=76e450a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyLDcqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyLDcqC.jpg&h=539007b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ig76mi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fig76mi0.jpg&h=f5cfad21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DLgnD5J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDLgnD5J.jpg&h=3f5e20b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"222fee4f9f2405bb24583cc22e42e5e0e73ba460","tid":1399493,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44feaf6d31f833bc0a96ba001d451195cddbce2b","tid":1399493,"uid":277873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci